links.title: Here's How Home Builder Stocks Might Fare Under a Biden or Trump Presidency
links.description: Home builders have seen a strong run over the past four years-and the outcome of the election might do little to change that. While President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden differ in broader policy, neither candidate's platforms appear likely to quell the robust housing demand that elevated builder stocks through the summer and early fall.
